tdCFK.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0.166},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/bBERGgCqgUPzriFxsVrXccINprn.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0.166},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/qAL0fwjZCQ41TwybgERAAUp4kWA.jpg","iso_639_1":"en","vote_average":0},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/v4E3Gb7QikastXcvKzvn519bM1m.jpg","iso_639_1":"fr","vote_average":0},{"width":2454,"height":1380,"file_path":"/e5H1SGeouEonsXHlQ6rEY8aAAWa.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/8Ff7BZCeeBBUFt7oKBUH2bWSTv1.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/9m8T8CUaz5M0S61JEw9k1j3y2G9.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0},{"width":1280,"height":720,"file_path":"/3Bpoz5guWB3LbdqFsHsNf7XV4Cr.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/zhVCJ14a1EbzfYQFUgyujcQZLuL.jpg","iso_639_1":"es","vote_average":0}]},"enriched_at":"2026-02-21T13:15:19.758+00:00","enrichment_cycle":1,"translations":[{"data":{"title":"Sakra","runtime":130,"tagline":"When a warrior belongs nowhere, the enemy is everywhere.","homepage":"","overview":"Qiao Feng is the respected leader of a roving band of martial artists. After he is wrongfully accused of murder and subsequently exiled, Qiao Feng goes on the run in search of answers about his own mysterious origin story—and the unknown enemies working to destroy him from the shadows."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"天龍八部之喬峰傳","runtime":130,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"北宋年間，丐幫幫主喬峰 (甄子丹 飾) 英雄俠義，受武林擁戴，卻突遭指認爲契丹人而衆叛親離。追尋身世，尋找仇人途中，喬峰與慕容家婢女阿朱 (陳鈺琪 飾) 相識相知，情愫互生。二人歷經聚賢莊、雁門關、鏡湖風波，直至阿朱因馬夫人 (王君馨 飾) 設計被喬峰錯殺，喬峰終查出一切皆是慕容復 (吳樾 飾) 爲復辟燕國的陰謀，喬峰憤而找上慕容複，誓要為阿朱報仇…."},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"HK","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"천룡팔부: 교봉전","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"북송 초기 송나라와 거란족의 요나라가 갈등을 겪던 시기를 배경으로, 거지 패거리 개방에 들어가 우두머리인 방주가 된 ‘교봉(견자단)’이 음모에 휩싸여 살인 누명을 쓰고 개방을 스스로 떠나면서 새롭게 시작되는 여정을 담은 정통 무협 액션"},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"天龍八部之喬峰傳","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"《天龍八部之喬峰傳》講述北宋年間，丐幫幫主喬峰（甄子丹 飾）英雄俠義，受武林擁戴，卻突遭指認爲外來入侵的契丹人而衆叛親離。追尋身世之謎，尋找仇人途中，喬峰與慕容家婢女阿朱（陳鈺琪 飾）相識相知，情愫互生。二人歷經聚賢莊、雁門關、鏡湖風波，直至阿朱因馬夫人（王君馨 飾）設計而被喬峰誤殺，喬峰終查出一切皆是慕容復（吳樾 飾）爲復辟燕國的陰謀，喬峰憤而找上慕容復，誓言報仇雪恨…."},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"天龙八部之乔峰传","runtime":132,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"北宋年间，丐帮帮主乔峰英雄侠义，受武林拥戴，却突遭指认为契丹人而众叛亲离。追寻身世，寻找仇人途中，乔峰与慕容家婢女阿朱相识相知，情愫互生。二人历经聚贤庄、雁门关、镜湖风波，直至阿朱因马夫人设计被乔峰错杀，乔峰终查出一切皆是慕容复为复辟燕国的阴谋，乔峰手刃慕容复，随后带着阿朱的遗愿孤身前往塞外。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Sakra","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"မြောက်ပိုင်း စုန့်မင်းဆက် အုပ်စိုးစဥ်အချိန်ကာလ သူတောင်းစားဂိုဏ်းရဲ့ဂိုဏ်းချုပ်ဖြစ်သူ ချောင်ဖုန်းဟာ သူရဲကောင်းတစ်ယောက်အဖြစ် သိုင်းလောကမှာ ကျော်ကြားခဲ့ပါတယ် ။ ဒါပေမဲ့ တစ်နေမှာတော့ ရုတ်တရက်ဆိုသလို ချီတန်း(မြောက်ပိုင်းတရုတ်နိုင်ငံရဲ့ လူမျိုးစုတစ်ခု) အဖြစ်စွပ်စွဲခြင်းခံရတဲ့အပြင် သစ္စာဖောက်အဖြစ် သိုင်းလောက လူတိုင်းက သတ်မှတ်ခဲ့ပါတော့တယ် ။ အမှန်တရားကို ရှာဖွေဖို့ သူတောင်းစားဂိုဏ်းကနေ ထွက်လာခဲ့ပြီး ခရီးလမ်းတစ်လျှောက်မှာ အညှိုးအတေးများကို ချောင်ဖုန်းတစ်ယောက် လက်စားချေခဲ့ပါတော့တယ် ။ အဲ့ဒီခရီးလမ်းမှာပဲ မုရုံအိမ်တော်မှမိန်းမလှလေး အားကျူးနဲ့ မေတ္တာမျှကာ အတူတူ သိုင်းလောကမှာ ကျဥ်လည်ခဲ့ပါတယ် ။ ဒါပေမဲ့ ကံကြမ္မာရဲ့ အလှည့်အပြောင်းတွေကို ခံလိုက်တဲ့အခါမှာတော့ –❏ ချောင်ဖုန်းတစ်ယောက် အဲ့ဒီအလှည့်အပြောင်းကို ဘယ်လိုရင်ဆိုင်မှာလဲ？❏ သူ့ရဲ့ ချစ်ရသူ မိန်းကလေး အားကျူးရဲ့ နောက်ကွယ်မှာ ဘယ်လိုအရာတွေရှိနေဦးမှာလဲ？❏ သစ္စာဖောက်အဖြစ် ခံယူထားရတဲ့ ချောင်ဖုန်းတစ်ယောက် သူကိုယ်တိုင်ရဲ့တရားမျှတမှုကို ပြန်လည်ရှာဖွေ နိုင်ပါ့မလားဆိုတာ ကြည့်ရှုလိုက်နော်။"},"name":"","iso_639_1":"my","iso_3166_1":"MY","english_name":"Burmese"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"เรื่องราวของเฉียวฟง ประมุขพรรคกระยาจก ผู้เชี่ยวชาญศิลปะการต่อสู้ และเป็นหนึ่งในบุคคลสําคัญของนิยายแปดเทพอสูรมังกรฟ้า เขาได้ถูกกล่าวหาเป็นชาวกิตัน ทรยศต่อพรรค ฆ่าหม่าต้าหยวน ฆ่าแม่ของตัวเอง และพระอาจารย์ที่สอนวรยุทธ เขาต้องพิสูจน์หาความจริง ต่อสู้กับเหล่าจอมยุทธ์ที่ตามฆ่า ขณะเดียวกันต้องปกป้องอาซู หญิงคนที่เขารัก เฉียวฟงรับบทโดยดอนนี่เยน โชว์ศิลปะการต่อสู้กังฟูได้อย่างโหดดิบเถื่อน รวมถึงฉากการต่อสู้ และองค์ประกอบต่างๆของภาพยนตร์ นําเสนอได้อย่างลงตัว สนุกและน่าตื่นตาตื่นใจมาก"},"name":"ภาษาไทย","iso_639_1":"th","iso_3166_1":"TH","english_name":"Thai"},{"data":{"title":"Sakra","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"فيلم حركة يحكي قصة زعيم عصابة متسولة ، Qiao Feng (دوني ين) المتهم بقتل زوج السيدة ما (غريس وونغ). نتيجة لذلك ، تم طرد Qiao Feng من عصابة المتسولين وهدد بالقتل."},"name":"العربية","iso_639_1":"ar","iso_3166_1":"SA","english_name":"Arabic"},{"data":{"title":"Thiên Long Bát Bộ: Kiều Phong Truyện","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Câu chuyện trong Thiên Long Bát Bộ: Kiều Phong Truyện sẽ diễn ra ở Tụ Hiền Trang, nơi Kiều Phong (Tiêu Phong - Chân Tử Đan đóng) bị quần hùng tìm ra chân tướng là người Khiết Đan, nghi là gián điệp và muốn sát hại chàng. Kiều Phong cũng rơi vào bẫy của Mộ Dung Phục, bị nghi đã giết chết phó bang chủ Cái Bang Mã Đại Nguyên. Mộ Dung Phục cũng sắp đặt khiến người yêu của Kiều Phong là A Châu (Trần Ngọc Kỳ) bị giết. Trước khi đánh, Kiều Phong lấy rượu ra uống xem như tuyệt giao với các bằng hữu trước đây. Trận chiến diễn ra, một mình Kiều Phong chống quần hùng, Hàng Long Thập Bát Chưởng lại một lần nữa uy trấn thiên hạ, đánh bại tất cả. Đây là sự kiện quy tụ nhiều cao thủ võ lâm trong Thiên Long Bát Bộ, cũng tạo bối cảnh tốt để Kiều Phong của Chân Tử Đan thỏa sức thể hiện khả năng võ thuật."},"name":"Tiếng Việt","iso_639_1":"vi","iso_3166_1":"VN","english_name":"Vietnamese"},{"data":{"title":"Hněv zrazeného válečníka","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Během dynastie Severního Sungu je Qiao Feng (Donnie Yen) vůdcem žebrácké sekty, který je nucen čelit dilematu svého osudu a životních zkušeností. Ve světě bojových umění spoléhá na svou sílu vůle bojovat ze všech sil v záblesku ostří. Toto je příběh o jeho životní cestě za sebeobjevováním, kdy se postupně mění v nejmocnějšího a nejodvážnějšího hrdinu."},"name":"Český","iso_639_1":"cs","iso_3166_1":"CZ","english_name":"Czech"},{"data":{"title":"Śakra, la légende des demi-dieux","runtime":130,"tagline":"Lorsqu’un guerrier n’a sa place nulle part, l’ennemi est partout.","homepage":"","overview":"Royaume de Chine, Xe siècle. Deux clans ennemis s'affrontent : les Song, dynastie royale, et les Khitan, peuple nomade guerrier. Qiao Feng du clan Song est un héros chevaleresque respecté, maître en arts martiaux. Accusé à tort d'avoir tué un chef de son propre clan, Qiao Feng est banni. Pour prouver son innocence, il s’engage dans un long périple, parsemé de combats extraordinaires, entre demi-dieux et semi-démons."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"Sakra","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Όταν ένας αξιοσέβαστος  ειδικός στις πολεμικές τέχνες  κατηγορείται για δολοφονία, ψάχνει απαντήσεις για τη δική του μυστηριώδη ιστορία καταγωγής και τους άγνωστους εχθρούς που εργάζονται για να τον καταστρέψουν."},"name":"ελληνικά","iso_639_1":"el","iso_3166_1":"GR","english_name":"Greek"},{"data":{"title":"Бесстрашный","runtime":131,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Уважаемый мастер после ложного обвинения и изгнания отправляется в путешествие, узнавая о своих корнях и всюду натыкаясь смертоносных врагов. Осиротевший в младенчестве Цяо Фэн воспитывается парой из Империи Сун. Мастерски освоив боевые искусства, он становится харизматичным главарем видной фракции – секты нищих. Внезапно выясняется его вражеское происхождение – и главу выгоняют, заодно обвинив в нескольких убийствах – военачальника и одного из старейшин организации, а также приемных родителей."},"name":"Pусский","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","english_name":"Russian"},{"data":{"title":"Donnie Yen's Sakra","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Song-Dynastie, China: Qiao Feng wurde als kleines Baby von einem armen Bauern-Ehepaar aufgenommen und großgezogen. Auch wenn er immer als der Ausgesetzte galt, hielt ihn das nie auf, ein großer Kämpfer zu werden. So wuchs er zu einem mächtigen Kampfkünstler heran und wurde eines Tages Anführer der rechtschaffenen Kampfkunstorganisation Beggars Gang. Fortan bewies er immer wieder Geschick und Loyalität, um sein Heimatland gegen ausländische Eindringlinge aus dem Norden zu verteidigen. Doch nicht nur in der Waffenkunst ist Feng ein Experte, auch das Bändigen von Wind und Feuer hat er gemeistert. Die Jahre seiner Siegeszüge sind jedoch nicht auf Dauer. Nachdem er einem Komplott zum Opfer fällt und seine Freunde und Kameraden sich von ihm abwenden, wird er erneut ein Ausgestoßener. Er setzt daraufhin alles daran, seine Ehre wieder herzustellen."},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","english_name":"German"},{"data":{"title":"Elárult harcos bosszúja","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Amikor egy ismert harcművészt gyilkossággal vádolnak, válaszokat keres saját rejtélyes történetének kérdéseire, és próbálja megtalálni az elpusztításán ügyködő ismeretlen ellenségeket."},"name":"Magyar","iso_639_1":"hu","iso_3166_1":"HU","english_name":"Hungarian"},{"data":{"title":"Sakra. Legenda wojownika","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Dynastia Song, Chiny: Qiao Feng (Donnie Yen) został przygarnięty i wychowany jako małe dziecko przez biedną parę wieśniaków. Mimo że zawsze był uważany za porzuconego, nigdy nie powstrzymało go to przed zostaniem wielkim wojownikiem. W ten sposób wyrósł na potężnego mistrza sztuk walki i pewnego dnia został przywódcą sprawiedliwej organizacji zajmującej się sztukami walki, Beggars Gang. Odtąd wielokrotnie wykazywał się umiejętnościami i lojalnością w obronie ojczyzny przed obcymi najeźdźcami z północy. Ale Feng jest nie tylko ekspertem w dziedzinie broni, ale także opanował poskramianie wiatru i ognia. Jednak lata jego triumfalnych marszów nie są trwałe. Po tym, jak pada ofiarą spisku, a przyjaciele i towarzysze odwracają się od niego, ponownie staje się wyrzutkiem. Następnie robi wszystko, aby przywrócić mu honor."},"name":"Polski","iso_639_1":"pl","iso_3166_1":"PL","english_name":"Polish"},{"data":{"title":"O Guerreiro Banido","runtime":0,"tagline":"Quando um guerreiro não pertence a lugar nenhum, o inimigo está em toda parte.","homepage":"","overview":"Qiao Feng, líder de uma seita de mendigos, é falsamente acusado e revelado como descendente Khitan. Expulso, ele busca limpar seu nome. Com Ah Zhu, que também procura suas origens, eles enfrentam desafios e inimigos desconhecidos."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"BR","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"Sakra","runtime":0,"tagline":"En busca de la verdad y el honor perdido","homepage":"","overview":"Cuando un artista marcial respetado es acusado de asesinato, emprende un viaje en busca de respuestas sobre su misterioso pasado y los enemigos que buscan destruirlo. A lo largo de su búsqueda, descubre detalles reveladores que podrían cambiar su vida para siempre."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"MX","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"Sakra","runtime":130,"tagline":"Ko bojevnik ne sodi nikamor, je sovražnik povsod.","homepage":"","overview":"Qiao Feng je spoštovan vodja potujoče skupine borcev borilnih veščin. Potem ko je po krivici obtožen umora ter izgnan, se Qiao Feng poda na pot v iskanju odgovorov o skrivnostni zgodbi lastnega porekla in o neznanih sovražnikih, ki ga iz ozadja poskušajo uničiti."},"name":"Slovenščina","iso_639_1":"sl","iso_3166_1":"SI","english_name":"Slovenian"},{"data":{"title":"Sakra","runtime":0,"tagline":"Bir savaşçı hiçbir yere ait değilse, düşman her yerdedir.","homepage":"","overview":"Qiao Feng, gezici dövüş sanatçılarından oluşan bir grubun saygın lideridir. Haksız yere cinayetle suçlanıp sürgüne gönderildikten sonra Qiao Feng, kendi gizemli köken hikayesi ve onu gölgelerden yok etmeye çalışan bilinmeyen düşmanlar hakkında cevaplar aramak için kaçmaya başlar."},"name":"Türkçe","iso_639_1":"tr","iso_3166_1":"TR","english_name":"Turkish"},{"data":{"title":"סאקרה","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"סרט אקשן הרפתקאות במנדרינית וקנטונית. כשאמן לחימה מכובד, (דוני יין, \"ייפ מן\", \"ג'ון ויק 4\") מואשם בהרג, הוא מסתובב ומחפש תשובות על סיפור המוצא המסתורי שלו ועל האויבים הלא ידועים הפועלים להשמידו."},"name":"עִבְרִית","iso_639_1":"he","iso_3166_1":"IL","english_name":"Hebrew"},{"data":{"title":"Sakra","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Basada en la clásica novela wuxia \"Demi-Gods and Semi-Devils\" de Louis Cha (conocido mundialmente por su seudónimo Jin Yong), SAKRA está protagonizada por Donnie Yen como Qiao Feng, el respetado líder de una banda ambulante de artistas marciales. Tras ser acusado injustamente de asesinato y posteriormente exiliado, Qiao Feng emprende una huida en busca de respuestas sobre su misterioso origen y los enemigos desconocidos que buscan destruirlo desde las sombras. A lo largo de su búsqueda, descubrirá detalles reveladores que podrían cambiar su vida para siempre."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"مقتدر","runtime":0,"tagline":"وقتی یک مبارز به هیچ‌ جا تعلق ندارد، دشمن همه جا هست.","homepage":"","overview":"چیائو فنگ رهبر مورد احترام گروهی سرگردان از رزمی‌کاران است. چیائو فنگ پس از اینکه به ناحق به قتل متهم و متعاقباً تبعید می‌شود، در جستجوی پاسخی در مورد داستان اصل و نسب رازآلود خود و دشمنان ناشناخته‌ای که در سایه‌ها به‌دنبال نابود کردن او هستند؛ دست به فرار می‌زند."},"name":"فارسی","iso_639_1":"fa","iso_3166_1":"IR","english_name":"Persian"},{"data":{"title":"Sakra","runtime":0,"tagline":"Kad ratnik ne pripada nigdje, neprijatelj je posvuda.","homepage":"","overview":"Cijenjeni gospodar, nakon što je lažno optužen i prognan, kreće na putovanje, upoznajući svoje korijene i nailazeći posvuda na smrtonosne neprijatelje. Siroče, Qiao Fenga, odgaja par iz Carstva Song. Savladavši borilačke vještine, postaje karizmatični vođa istaknute frakcije - sekte prosjaka. Iznenada se otkrije njegovo neprijateljsko podrijetlo - a poglavar biva izbačen, istovremeno optužujući vojskovođu i jednog od starješina organizacije, kao i njegove posvojitelje, za nekoliko ubojstava."},"name":"Hrvatski","iso_639_1":"hr","iso_3166_1":"HR","english_name":"Croatian"},{"data":{"title":"シャクラ","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"“宇宙最強”の異名を持つ俳優ドニー・イェンが、自ら製作・監督・主演を務めた武侠アクション映画。中華圏を代表する小説家・金庸の長編小説『天龍八部』を原作に、無敵の武芸者・喬峯の活躍を壮大な世界観で描いている。"},"name":"日本語","iso_639_1":"ja","iso_3166_1":"JP","english_name":"Japanese"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"SG","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"PT","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"CA","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Український","iso_639_1":"uk","iso_3166_1":"UA","english_name":"Ukrainian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"","iso_639_1":"tl","iso_3166_1":"PH","english_name":"Tagalog"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Bahasa indonesia","iso_639_1":"id","iso_3166_1":"ID","english_name":"Indonesian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Bahasa melayu","iso_639_1":"ms","iso_3166_1":"MY","english_name":"Malay"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"العربية","iso_639_1":"ar","iso_3166_1":"AE","english_name":"Arabic"},{"data":{"title":"Sakra - La leggenda dei semidei","runtime":0,"tagline":"Quando un guerriero non appartiene a nessun luogo, il nemico è ovunque.","homepage":"","overview":"Quando un rispettato artista marziale viene accusato di essere un assassino, va in giro alla ricerca di risposte sulla sua misteriosa storia di origine e sui nemici sconosciuti che lavorano per distruggerlo."},"name":"Italiano","iso_639_1":"it","iso_3166_1":"IT","english_name":"Italian"},{"data":{"title":"Sakra","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Quan un respectat artista marcial és acusat d’assassinat, recorre d’un costat a l’altre la recerca de respostes sobre la seva misteriosa història d’origen i els enemics que treballen per destruir-lo."},"name":"Català","iso_639_1":"ca","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Catalan"}],"reviews_tmdb":[{"id":"640b7ff8d95420007b675380","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/640b7ff8d95420007b675380","author":"terrapong","content":"Another mixed bag from Donnie Yen.\r\n\r\nWhile the martial arts and fight choreography are fun, the movie itself is boring and incoherent. It feels like a hundred episode TV drama cut into 2 hours of random clips. The amount of nonsense in this movie completely overshadows the good action scenes, which is disappointing.","created_at":"2023-03-10T19:07:36.210Z","updated_at":"2023-03-10T19:12:05.213Z","author_details":{"name":"","rating":5,"username":"terrapong","avatar_path":null}},{"id":"640f8b442a09bc00866c3612","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/640f8b442a09bc00866c3612","author":"MovieGuys","content":"Sakra is a mixed bag at best. Well choreographed, martial arts action  sequences, are \"cut and pasted\" into an inarticulate, meandering, disjointed film, with a weak, plot hole ridden, back story, derived from ancient Chinese folk lore, linked to the beggars clan. \r\n\r\nDonnie Yen and a larger cast of Hong Kong actors, can't save this film from its conspicuous shortcomings. \r\n\r\nIn summary, this is a mediocre effort at best. Its moderately watchable but the dismal back story, combined with a general lack of cohesion is more a frustrating, than enjoyable watch.","created_at":"2023-03-13T20:44:52.228Z","updated_at":"2023-03-13T20:47:44.074Z","author_details":{"name":"","rating":5,"username":"MovieGuys","avatar_path":null}},{"id":"6453d2aac0442901016202ce","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/6453d2aac0442901016202ce","author":"Chris Sawin","content":"_Sakra_ is a really fun action film trapped within the confines of a convoluted melodrama which is mostly only worthwhile if you’re a hardcore fan of wuxia films or a Yen enthusiast.\r\n\r\nThe martial arts legend has a strong on-screen presence and is as talented as ever when it comes to anything martial arts related, but _Sakra_ drags its feet with its storytelling, meandering aimlessly between spurts of heavy action.\r\n\r\nFull review: https://boundingintocomics.com/2023/04/21/sakra-review-donnie-yen-establishes-himself-as-a-wuxia-god/","created_at":"2023-05-04T15:43:38.719Z","updated_at":"2023-05-04T15:43:38.810Z","author_details":{"name":"Chris Sawin","rating":6,"username":"ChrisSawin","avatar_path":null}}],"recommendations":[{"id":965244,"adult":false,"title":"Ghost in the Shell: SAC_2045 Sustainable War","video":false,"overview":"In the year 2045, after an economic disaster known as the Synchronized Global Default, rapid developments in AI propelled the world to enter a state of \"Sustainable War\". However, the public is not aware of the threat that AI has towards the human race.  A compilation film with newly added footage.","genre_ids":[16,28,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.1731,"vote_count":75,"poster_path":"/kNTvGWDTxb2spAp9SRLNfOo7kCM.jpg","release_date":"2021-12-21","vote_average":6.807,"backdrop_path":"/htLu9YpLJCXk56GAHuFDnj8oadV.jpg","original_title":"攻殻機動隊 SAC_2045 持続可能戦争","original_language":"ja"},{"id":864120,"adult":false,"title":"Tzadik","video":false,"overview":"In 1942, Red Army officer Nikolai Kiselyov receives orders to evacuate over 200 Jewish women, children, and elderly men facing brutality and death in Nazi-occupied Belarus. These exhausted, starving, terrified and bereaved people, deeply scarred by the horrors they have witnessed, must trek hundreds of kilometers along forest paths to regain hope of survival and faith in the future.","genre_ids":[10752,18,36],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.491,"vote_count":13,"poster_path":"/fKYKDJalagPq0pIcDwWDB4j16in.jpg","release_date":"2023-02-16","vote_average":7.2,"backdrop_path":"/8oBiwDXzpaaGYJjWGRtIQ1kSLaX.jpg","original_title":"Праведник","original_language":"ru"},{"id":986252,"adult":false,"title":"A Murder Erased","video":false,"overview":"International narcotics officer CHOI , has been demoted by his superior officer MA to local duties after partaking in bribery in the line of work. He’s assigned to a death scene investigation by YAN where the deceased, YUNG’s body had laid undiscovered for eight years, and only recently discovered by maintenance workers during the renovation of an old block of flat. CHOI looks into CHAO as the prime suspect, and linking it to adultery with YUNG’s widow PING as an accomplice. The case soon comes under scrutiny by a high-ranking court prosecutor SANTOS. Under his inquiries, the investigator becomes the investigated, and CHOI’s actions fall under suspicion as all manner of inconsistencies come to light from his statement. YUNG was a man of many vices, with few crimes left untouched by his hand – rape, drug smuggling, blackmail and working alongside notorious gangster FAI WAI.","genre_ids":[80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.4772,"vote_count":5,"poster_path":"/dZWdBV1Zsqlw21mQAtlAvaMm1Mx.jpg","release_date":"2022-06-16","vote_average":6,"backdrop_path":"/zwQxffCq74Fhgs2ch98M3sRYUBb.jpg","original_title":"被消失的凶案","original_language":"cn"},{"id":802068,"adult":false,"title":"Wild Dog","video":false,"overview":"Wild Dog aka Vijay Varma is an NIA agent who’s brought back to field from a desk job to handle a terrorism case. Despite having a personal motive, he moves heaven and earth to ensure justice is served for the sake of the country.","genre_ids":[28,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.3755,"vote_count":21,"poster_path":"/8377XckHbfJDMrkSpEa9ZQJlVE0.jpg","release_date":"2021-04-02","vote_average":5.6,"backdrop_path":"/bdZS1xmow1avubmpM0p0GXkQaGE.jpg","original_title":"Wild Dog","original_language":"te"},{"id":611186,"adult":false,"title":"Tales of the Bizarre: 2019 Rain Special","video":false,"overview":"","genre_ids":[27,53,9648,10770],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.5498,"vote_count":2,"poster_path":"/cfUnGHW4Q8qG5VS0qBBxEj8ooe0.jpg","release_date":"2019-06-08","vote_average":5,"backdrop_path":"/j1EwW0s6jpGifg7W8DRVERJW8AL.jpg","original_title":"世にも奇妙な物語 ’19雨の特別編","original_language":"ja"},{"id":1093485,"adult":false,"title":"The White Storm 3: Heaven or Hell","video":false,"overview":"An undercover cop who invade a drug cartel led by a notorious Thai drug lord. In classic heroic bloodshed fashion, the two develop a bond of brotherhood.","genre_ids":[28,80,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.5178,"vote_count":63,"poster_path":"/xtsEksiUjysMYv4gxdRQcbu2v6V.jpg","release_date":"2023-07-06","vote_average":6.135,"backdrop_path":"/eWxTNCLRElAXsnYRIkjeJNRe9Jn.jpg","original_title":"掃毒3︰人在天涯","original_language":"cn"},{"id":45491,"adult":false,"title":"Sex and Zen","video":false,"overview":"A recently married scholar goes on a quest for knowledge of other people's wives, based on his philosophical differences with the Sack Monk. He encounters the Flying Thief, who agrees to help him find women, but only if he attains a penis as big as a horse's. The scholar has a surgeon attach said unit, and he's off and running on his mission, only to find that there are obstacles to his new lifestyle, such as jealous husbands and treacherous females.","genre_ids":[18,35,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.9147,"vote_count":99,"poster_path":"/tQMf9iPeCsrkeSXxkNKtY1R82mx.jpg","release_date":"1991-11-30","vote_average":6,"backdrop_path":"/onCcMjFXrO8InXVsaCMbiHuucqa.jpg","original_title":"玉蒲團之偷情寶鑑","original_language":"cn"},{"id":97642,"adult":false,"title":"Tokyo Species","video":false,"overview":"Michiko a high school girl had committed suicide, but she was resuscitated by an alien parasitism. While she brutally murdered men and spawned one after another, her friend Rika met Mayumi. Mayumi was told that she was parasitized by a gentle alien. They decided to fight Michiko.","genre_ids":[27,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.1484,"vote_count":35,"poster_path":"/k0pjzrJsycggkylHYj9PckdCgwQ.jpg","release_date":"2012-02-03","vote_average":5.686,"backdrop_path":"/dnnMQstoMrnYvKctZXJKlgetU0k.jpg","original_title":"TOKYOスピーシーズ","original_language":"ja"},{"id":698215,"adult":false,"title":"HOKUSAI","video":false,"overview":"The unknown life of Ukiyo-e artist Katsushika Hokusai in the Edo period, who is said to have painted more than 30,000 works throughout his life, such as \"Thirty-Six Views of Mount Fuji\"","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.7327,"vote_count":47,"poster_path":"/AgPcFBUUuYsWSHewO9Wg70IQ7eG.jpg","release_date":"2021-05-29","vote_average":6.511,"backdrop_path":"/6XxOcUSP1bVBJg0jBY6YNyWRGns.jpg","original_title":"HOKUSAI","original_language":"ja"},{"id":998731,"adult":false,"title":"Sasaki and Miyano: Graduation","video":false,"overview":"As Sasaki prepares for his college entrance exams, Miyano tries to make the most of their limited time together while grappling with his own emotions.","genre_ids":[16,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.7378,"vote_count":44,"poster_path":"/xjZjNaUVF9mX7ekOL3lvBUi72eQ.jpg","release_date":"2023-02-17","vote_average":5.9,"backdrop_path":"/jMSZsWqICQAhkrne31yjHJgzhfR.jpg","original_title":"映画 佐々木と宮野ー卒業編ー","original_language":"ja"},{"id":1079394,"adult":false,"title":"The Five","video":false,"overview":"A scorned woman enlists the help of five strangers to execute a bank robbery. Tensions rise as the men anxiously await her arrival with the money, leaving the crew to wonder if they have been betrayed.","genre_ids":[37],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.4674,"vote_count":44,"poster_path":"/xckDPGprPVDpuzhSyo9E7SZJ2wa.jpg","release_date":"2023-01-07","vote_average":5.9,"backdrop_path":"/jkBFGhuJKLH8VurXqVKQ2mxvVYC.jpg","original_title":"The Five","original_language":"en"},{"id":950141,"adult":false,"title":"Organ Trail","video":false,"overview":"A young Abigale Archer is left friendless and alone in a brutal Montana winter during the 1870s—fighting for survival and to retrieve her one earthly possession, her family’s horse, from a gang of bloodthirsty bandits.","genre_ids":[27,37,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.6406,"vote_count":98,"poster_path":"/s9nwiVMOVvnS2Jt6hdy7UHoFSD0.jpg","release_date":"2023-04-14","vote_average":6.082,"backdrop_path":"/dE1SUD70ptplI0bKbdQCbbS8RZ0.jpg","original_title":"Organ Trail","original_language":"en"},{"id":734253,"adult":false,"title":"Adipurush","video":false,"overview":"7000 years ago, Ayodhya's Prince Raghava and Prince Sesh along with the Mighty Vanar Warriors travels to the island of Lanka with an aim to rescue Raghava's wife Janaki, who has been abducted by Lankesh, the king of Lanka.","genre_ids":[28,12,14],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.7097,"vote_count":103,"poster_path":"/1H2xEZOixs0z0JKwyjANZiKNNVJ.jpg","release_date":"2023-06-16","vote_average":4.68,"backdrop_path":"/xjjHH1SxphgYtwCCdAlN5wmYGqR.jpg","original_title":"आदिपुरुष","original_language":"hi"},{"id":726274,"adult":false,"title":"Irati","video":false,"overview":"Western Pyrenees, year 778. When his land is threatened by the ruthless armies of the Frankish emperor, a Basque warlord asks for help from his ancestral gods.","genre_ids":[18,12,14],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.717,"vote_count":103,"poster_path":"/jVUpT8PIWU9mpUWQqEyYDqmFN2y.jpg","release_date":"2023-02-24","vote_average":6.6,"backdrop_path":"/2UsNQV74s3lvw8XdI13KTxExZ2K.jpg","original_title":"Irati","original_language":"eu"},{"id":20878,"adult":false,"title":"Kidnapping, Caucasian Style","video":false,"overview":"Shurik, a kind but naïve ethnography student, falls in love with the intelligent, athletic and beautiful All-Union Leninist Young Communist League member Nina. He has a rival in the wealthy comrade Saakhov, who concocts a kidnapping scheme to force Nina to marry him.","genre_ids":[35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.3829,"vote_count":272,"poster_path":"/orp7Ec8fDDHXFYnAjOPWsuF0Dhe.jpg","release_date":"1967-04-03","vote_average":7.667,"backdrop_path":"/uAvOQFEUYdYEM9J29EKIywRU9kB.jpg","original_title":"Кавказская пленница, или Новые приключения Шурика","original_language":"ru"},{"id":264859,"adult":false,"title":"Six Swedish Girls in Alps","video":false,"overview":"This comedy has everyone's favorite 6 Swedish gals enjoying their stay in the alps. When the girls aren't enjoying the pleasure of their own company they're out having a good time with nearly everyone else in town.","genre_ids":[10749,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.9246,"vote_count":61,"poster_path":"/l5Ks2f3lEPsJR0YrzZXOvETNrhi.jpg","release_date":"1983-07-22","vote_average":6.4,"backdrop_path":"/dLfPOTB9zlGCNZJinYvf9yygaX6.jpg","original_title":"Sechs Schwedinnen auf der Alm","original_language":"de"},{"id":695282,"adult":false,"title":"Take Back","video":false,"overview":"Zara and Brian are living the perfect small town life when a mysterious stranger from Zara's secret past kidnaps their daughter and now they must race to save her life.","genre_ids":[28,53,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.7132,"vote_count":70,"poster_path":"/16JXKkATNiSKouOhxyg9lkHBag9.jpg","release_date":"2021-06-18","vote_average":5.943,"backdrop_path":"/10NS0wKi2kKDTzMQIBV7TTMlxDP.jpg","original_title":"Take Back","original_language":"en"},{"id":17618,"adult":false,"title":"Laid to Rest","video":false,"overview":"A young girl wakes up in a casket with a head injury and no memory of her identity. She quickly realizes she was abducted by a serial killer and she must fight to survive.","genre_ids":[53,27],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.7566,"vote_count":232,"poster_path":"/7bmcFvPGG3csVoefHKyiH1L5hh2.jpg","release_date":"2009-03-18","vote_average":5.403,"backdrop_path":"/44uSXtdM6fgohWLcN8cl4eJ2PwX.jpg","original_title":"Laid to Rest","original_language":"en"},{"id":1149381,"adult":false,"title":"Soulcatcher","video":false,"overview":"A military contractor hired to seize a weapon that turns people into savage killers seeks revenge when his brother falls victim to the device.","genre_ids":[28,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.8987,"vote_count":283,"poster_path":"/l1f9JSPjCfNftigEii1SDK1g2b3.jpg","release_date":"2023-08-02","vote_average":6.348,"backdrop_path":"/oPYJ1artbj7x8zgpJJkQMp0mNTW.jpg","original_title":"Operacja: Soulcatcher","original_language":"pl"},{"id":606403,"adult":false,"title":"Special Delivery","video":false,"overview":"A black-market cabbie drives criminals at breakneck speeds until she is left in charge of a fugitive's son.","genre_ids":[28,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.6063,"vote_count":205,"poster_path":"/iFUBAfMDlFOck29BEwS1awH5TB3.jpg","release_date":"2022-01-12","vote_average":7,"backdrop_path":"/e2rPSd0yZGwAQzZYEcI21hDMy0C.jpg","original_title":"특송","original_language":"ko"}],"similar_content":[{"id":246926,"adult":false,"title":"Bruce and Shaolin Kung Fu","video":false,"overview":"Japanese forces in Shanghai attempt to destroy the patriotic spirit of the Chinese by closing down all Kung Fu gyms. Chang Ling (Bruce Le), a top Chinese Kung Fu practitioner, is forced to flee to Korea. The Japanese forces pursue him there, and so Chang Ling fights back, defeating many Japanese fighters before finally encountering the Japanese commander.","genre_ids":[28],"popularity":0.1667,"vote_count":3,"poster_path":"/zCwQKc6BnPP1cnSMsQZkJnMOOEv.jpg","release_date":"1977-03-19","vote_average":7,"backdrop_path":"/jSuxiXIYDIBHv4qioYXVRozDhqQ.jpg","original_title":"Bruce and Shaolin Kung Fu","original_language":"cn"},{"id":1291785,"adult":false,"title":"Twilight of the Warriors: Dragon Throne","video":false,"overview":"The second installment of the Twilight of the Warriors trilogy.\r In 1950s Hong Kong, brothers Lui Cheng-tung and Chen Jim fled to the lawless Kowloon Walled City at the peak of their careers. They endured hardships, waiting for a chance to reclaim their losses. During this time, they encountered a man who significantly influenced their struggle to regain what they had lost.","genre_ids":[28,53,80,12],"popularity":0.7488,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/5D4Ss05hIbV7E8fjO4ZThLbGa6J.jpg","release_date":"","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"九龍城寨之龍頭","original_language":"cn"},{"id":1291787,"adult":false,"title":"Twilight of the Warriors: The Final Chapter","video":false,"overview":"The final installment of the Twilight of the Warriors trilogy.","genre_ids":[28,53,80],"popularity":0.2766,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/5D4Ss05hIbV7E8fjO4ZThLbGa6J.jpg","release_date":"","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"九龍城寨之終章","original_language":"cn"},{"id":646,"adult":false,"title":"Dr. No","video":false,"overview":"Agent 007 battles mysterious Dr. No, a scientific genius bent on destroying the U.S. space program. As the countdown to disaster begins, Bond must go to Jamaica, where he encounters beautiful Honey Ryder, to confront a megalomaniacal villain in his massive island headquarters.","genre_ids":[12,28,53],"popularity":7.2117,"vote_count":3956,"poster_path":"/f9HsemSsBEHN5eoMble1bj6fDxs.jpg","release_date":"1962-10-07","vote_average":6.991,"backdrop_path":"/ptcXbbxTyjHfEE4d4QocNP0YQct.jpg","original_title":"Dr. No","original_language":"en"},{"id":657,"adult":false,"title":"From Russia with Love","video":false,"overview":"Agent 007 is back in the second installment of the James Bond series, this time battling a secret crime organization known as SPECTRE. Russians Rosa Klebb and Kronsteen are out to snatch a decoding device known as the Lektor, using the ravishing Tatiana to lure Bond into helping them. Bond willingly travels to meet Tatiana in Istanbul, where he must rely on his wits to escape with his life in a series of deadly encounters with the enemy.","genre_ids":[28,53,12],"popularity":6.5294,"vote_count":3279,"poster_path":"/zx4V17FP8oclNvOpTgs2iCCtiYk.jpg","release_date":"1963-10-10","vote_average":7.065,"backdrop_path":"/8JMiQa0OqsCYvbNUrQIrMzwV7g2.jpg","original_title":"From Russia with Love","original_language":"en"},{"id":658,"adult":false,"title":"Goldfinger","video":false,"overview":"Special agent 007 comes face to face with one of the most notorious villains of all time, and now he must outwit and outgun the powerful tycoon to prevent him from cashing in on a devious scheme to raid Fort Knox -- and obliterate the world's economy.","genre_ids":[12,28,53],"popularity":6.2145,"vote_count":3871,"poster_path":"/aKNFzaqQgPzsGXnsMc4kJH5hFIV.jpg","release_date":"1964-09-20","vote_average":7.355,"backdrop_path":"/f1Is9VLQZSRpeLMU7mIcj5aXclt.jpg","original_title":"Goldfinger","original_language":"en"},{"id":667,"adult":false,"title":"You Only Live Twice","video":false,"overview":"A mysterious spacecraft captures Russian and American space capsules and brings the two superpowers to the brink of war. James Bond investigates the case in Japan and comes face to face with his archenemy Blofeld.","genre_ids":[28,53,12],"popularity":7.1355,"vote_count":2402,"poster_path":"/fdRbvRcEXcf2rC4ghLFZzCWPSmB.jpg","release_date":"1967-06-13","vote_average":6.593,"backdrop_path":"/cpZAXIYA0lkZMpAt7d1MmH8ojNV.jpg","original_title":"You Only Live Twice","original_language":"en"},{"id":668,"adult":false,"title":"On Her Majesty's Secret Service","video":false,"overview":"With the help of Marc-Ange Draco, head of the Unione Corse crime syndicate, and Draco's troubled daughter Tracy, James Bond tracks his archnemesis, Ernst Stravro Blofeld, to a mountaintop retreat in the Swiss Alps, where he is training an army of beautiful, lethal women.","genre_ids":[12,28,53],"popularity":5.3271,"vote_count":2077,"poster_path":"/m3KfbxvqaiAvRJ6MpguA3GuLdDQ.jpg","release_date":"1969-12-18","vote_average":6.562,"backdrop_path":"/58pMrmwwcKamJIdjUlinE6QX1Fs.jpg","original_title":"On Her Majesty's Secret Service","original_language":"en"},{"id":682,"adult":false,"title":"The Man with the Golden Gun","video":false,"overview":"Cool government operative James Bond searches for a stolen invention that can turn the sun's heat into a destructive weapon. He soon crosses paths with the menacing Francisco Scaramanga, a hitman so skilled he has a seven-figure working fee. Bond then joins forces with the swimsuit-clad Mary Goodnight, and together they track Scaramanga to a Thai tropical isle hideout where the killer-for-hire lures the slick spy into a deadly maze for a final duel.","genre_ids":[12,28,53],"popularity":4.9709,"vote_count":2220,"poster_path":"/xVkbKwGnBVNQ122GN5bCTMyPbWz.jpg","release_date":"1974-12-04","vote_average":6.456,"backdrop_path":"/3tpNEbRahT8smy7RraaWa0xg9Gv.jpg","original_title":"The Man with the Golden Gun","original_language":"en"},{"id":691,"adult":false,"title":"The Spy Who Loved Me","video":false,"overview":"Russian and British submarines with nuclear missiles on board both vanish from sight without a trace. England and Russia both blame each other as James Bond tries to solve the riddle of the disappearing ships. But the KGB also has an agent on the case.","genre_ids":[12,28,53],"popularity":5.5757,"vote_count":2166,"poster_path":"/3ZxHKFxMYvAko680DsRgAZKWcLi.jpg","release_date":"1977-07-07","vote_average":6.825,"backdrop_path":"/8lRdfsmJjUXQU3DMOOB3vVIhJxP.jpg","original_title":"The Spy Who Loved Me","original_language":"en"},{"id":698,"adult":false,"title":"Moonraker","video":false,"overview":"After Drax Industries' Moonraker space shuttle is hijacked, secret agent James Bond is assigned to investigate, traveling to California to meet the company's owner, the mysterious Hugo Drax. With the help of scientist Dr. Holly Goodhead, Bond soon uncovers Drax's nefarious plans for humanity, all the while fending off an old nemesis, Jaws, and venturing to Venice, Rio, the Amazon...and even outer space.","genre_ids":[28,12,53,878],"popularity":5.3553,"vote_count":2152,"poster_path":"/6LrJdXNmu5uHOVALZxVYd44Lva0.jpg","release_date":"1979-06-26","vote_average":6.181,"backdrop_path":"/mrDC5DLx2wljt4HZGwgkmqlzfcF.jpg","original_title":"Moonraker","original_language":"en"},{"id":2004,"adult":false,"title":"Kebab Connection","video":false,"overview":"In Hamburg, Ibrahim \"Ibo\" Secmez, of Turkish descent, wants to direct the first German kung-fu movie. For now, he makes commercials for his uncle's kebab restaurant. Titzie, an aspiring actress and Ibo's German girlfriend, finds she's pregnant. Ibo is uncertain about fatherhood - compounded by his father's disowning him for getting a German girl pregnant - so Titzie sends him packing. He makes attempts at getting it right, but as the birth approaches, he's still not ready. In the background are three thugs in search of good tripe soup and a Capulet-Montegue feud between the kebab joint and a Greek taverna across the street. Can Ibo be the glove upon that hand?","genre_ids":[35,28,10749],"popularity":0.3216,"vote_count":71,"poster_path":"/jNHsAVtJEzAGQJnv3AGagBSAFLu.jpg","release_date":"2004-04-21","vote_average":6.655,"backdrop_path":"/s2XyJwZ2nmtbCT8ZE3oPlm0yq1j.jpg","original_title":"Kebab Connection","original_language":"de"},{"id":2019,"adult":false,"title":"Hard Target","video":false,"overview":"When a woman's father goes missing, she enlists a local to aid in her search.  The pair soon discover that her father has died at the hands of a wealthy sportsman who hunts homeless men as a form of recreation.","genre_ids":[28,53,80],"popularity":4.5029,"vote_count":1306,"poster_path":"/mXCM7pmUFUGp7QzSmare3RITe6n.jpg","release_date":"1993-04-27","vote_average":6.48,"backdrop_path":"/4IRHnS9Ljvb4tGI2SGaSiQikcaE.jpg","original_title":"Hard Target","original_language":"en"},{"id":2043,"adult":false,"title":"Along Came a Spider","video":false,"overview":"After the harrowing death of his partner, forensic psychologist and best-selling author Alex Cross cannot forgive himself and has retreated to the peace of retirement. But when a brilliant criminal kidnaps a senator's young daughter, he is lured back into action as the kidnapper wants to deal with Alex personally. Teamed with Jezzie Flanigan, the Secret Service agent assigned to protect the missing girl, Alex follows a serpentine trail of clues that leads him to a stunning discovery - the kidnapper wants more than just ransom.","genre_ids":[80,9648,53,28],"popularity":2.9077,"vote_count":2000,"poster_path":"/svXTe3qxlV4oqAe0NoUN1rMXKB7.jpg","release_date":"2001-04-06","vote_average":6.339,"backdrop_path":"/5C6njaciKvyZlKWUrQX7mjdl4D1.jpg","original_title":"Along Came a Spider","original_language":"en"},{"id":2048,"adult":false,"title":"I, Robot","video":false,"overview":"In 2035, where robots are commonplace and abide by the three laws of robotics, a technophobic cop investigates an apparent suicide. Suspecting that a robot may be responsible for the death, his investigation leads him to believe that humanity may be in danger.","genre_ids":[28,878],"popularity":7.874,"vote_count":12454,"poster_path":"/efwv6F2lGaghjPpBRSINHtoEiZB.jpg","release_date":"2004-07-15","vote_average":6.959,"backdrop_path":"/lOXVbF2mBK0xUt8sLInF3TIk5YS.jpg","original_title":"I, Robot","original_language":"en"},{"id":251516,"adult":false,"title":"Kung Fury","video":false,"overview":"During an unfortunate series of events, a friend of Kung Fury is assassinated by the most dangerous kung fu master criminal of all time, Adolf Hitler, a.k.a Kung Führer.  Kung Fury decides to travel back in time to Nazi Germany in order to kill Hitler and end the Nazi empire once and for all.","genre_ids":[28,35,878,14],"popularity":1.2392,"vote_count":1921,"poster_path":"/f1QpIlCqlFXp1hjnLplXb5irxip.jpg","release_date":"2015-05-22","vote_average":7.472,"backdrop_path":"/gdxPHC5nw9sBrrUyiOnzkWqnLE4.jpg","original_title":"Kung Fury","original_language":"en"},{"id":251532,"adult":false,"title":"Master Of Guangdong Hall","video":false,"overview":"The evil Dong Won has unbeatable kicking legs and proudly travels the land proving his expertise. But when a young man loses his foster parent to Won's deadly kick, he seeks out an old drunken master to learn a way to defeat the Master of the Leg.","genre_ids":[28,18],"popularity":0.1682,"vote_count":2,"poster_path":"/sF4q4QCIKdrxvSulYcs3TWu1lGS.jpg","release_date":"1983-03-15","vote_average":5.5,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"광동관소화자","original_language":"ko"},{"id":877,"adult":false,"title":"Scarface","video":false,"overview":"In 1920s Chicago, Italian immigrant and notorious thug, Antonio 'Tony' Camonte, aka Scarface, shoots his way to the top of the mobs while trying to protect his sister from the criminal life.","genre_ids":[80,28,18],"popularity":2.9383,"vote_count":670,"poster_path":"/y4E5oRiHMTFkEB12IIcpbKbKzDW.jpg","release_date":"1932-04-09","vote_average":7.416,"backdrop_path":"/3i6H4cVfvWh55sN1iXyeb8Q50nY.jpg","original_title":"Scarface","original_language":"en"},{"id":916,"adult":false,"title":"Bullitt","video":false,"overview":"Senator Walter Chalmers is aiming to take down mob boss Pete Ross with the help of testimony from the criminal's hothead brother Johnny, who is in protective custody in San Francisco under the watch of police lieutenant Frank Bullitt. When a pair of mob hitmen enter the scene, Bullitt follows their trail through a maze of complications and double-crosses. This thriller includes one of the most famous car chases ever filmed.","genre_ids":[28,80,53],"popularity":4.1665,"vote_count":1255,"poster_path":"/2ffzF1WmeXtH420fSUoCrecFvDA.jpg","release_date":"1968-10-17","vote_average":7.143,"backdrop_path":"/iKO7UEnXJUumjbjNwP4719n7vds.jpg","original_title":"Bullitt","original_language":"en"},{"id":421790,"adult":false,"title":"Gladiator for Rent","video":false,"overview":"The owner of the private detective agency Ilya Mirsky receives a tempting offer from the wife of media mogul Eva Lukachyova - he should not allow the leak of compromising information, which would deprive Eva of her multimillion-dollar inheritance. Deciding to take the case, Ilya could have hardly imagined that he would have to face a whole series of sophisticated murder, and that the result would be in the danger of his own life.","genre_ids":[9648,28,80],"popularity":0.189,"vote_count":2,"poster_path":"/ySqSAVCGBvDVEzBhvkxS9akV8bP.jpg","release_date":"1993-05-31","vote_average":8.5,"backdrop_path":"/gLQMAlFd4hzrhy68vMmgiO46ZBF.jpg","original_title":"Гладиатор по найму","original_language":"ru"}],"external_ids":{"imdb_id":"tt22488024","twitter_id":null,"facebook_id":null,"wikidata_id":"Q115599751","instagram_id":null},"social_ids":{"twitter":null,"facebook":null,"instagram":null},"gdvg_id":110265,"wiki_plot":null,"wiki_synopsis":null,"wiki_episode_guide":null,"wiki_production":null,"wiki_cast_notes":null,"wiki_reception":null,"wiki_soundtrack":null,"wiki_release":null,"wiki_accolades":null,"release_dates":[{"iso_3166_1":"BR","release_dates":[{"note":"","type":4,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2025-06-30T00:00:00.000Z","certification":""}]},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","release_dates":[{"note":"","type":4,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2023-01-21T00:00:00.000Z","certification":""}]},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","release_dates":[{"note":"Fantasy Filmfest Nights","type":1,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2023-04-20T00:00:00.000Z","certification":""},{"note":"